up that fasty I scored, only needing (so far) brakes and new fuel lines
to tear up the road, even the tires are new on a 30k mile OE everything.
Backing up a previous post on the matter, unless 50,00 frenchmen swear
by the guy, build it your damn self. Seems we're the only ones who care
